#13301
Rufus trainer academy~
Rufus~
Rufus stands vigil here over the academy grounds.
~
An ancient knight wise in the ways of war, Rufus has volunteered his time to
the training of new wouldbe adventures.  Though ravaged by time only the most
foolhardy would challenge him to combat, as he performs his duties with the
blessings of the gods, whom it would not be wise to anger.
~
