#ROOMS
#13301
A Whole New World~
Welcome to Amethyst.  You are standing in a room in which the gods of Amethyst
have posted several signs to help those new to this realm.  If you feel 
confident that you know the basics you may proceed downwards to recieve your
equipment.  To look at the sign, type &OLOOK SIGN&z.  Remember the world of
Amethyst is newly formed, so if you experience trouble please be patient, also
if you need help, or have questions, or even wish to make a suggestion, don't
hesitate to contact an immortal.
~
~
0 0 13
D5
~
~
0 -1 13302
E
sign~
Amethyst consists of several "rooms" that allow movement within the basic
directions north, south, east, west, northwest, northeast, southwest, and
southeast.  Standard abreviations of n, s, e, w, sw, se, nw, ne, d, and up may
also be used.
For other topics that may be of interest to a new adventurer, type &OLOOK GUIDE
&z for a list of topics or see &OHELP COMBAT&z, and &OHELP RULES&z.
~
S
#13302
Amethyst Mud Academy~
You have entered into the main part of the academy.  Below you lies the town
square of New Hope.  You should only proceed this way if you are truely
prepared as there is currently no way to return to the academy.  To the east,
there is a room where you may practice skills.  It is recommended that you
visit the trainer first thing.  To the west is a store that sells a few 
essential supplies, while to the north you can proceed to practice the basics
of combat and gain a set of equipment.
~
~
