#13303
Academy Training Room~
You have entered into a large room to one side of the academy.  Judging from 
the appearance of this room, it is used frequently, as all of the equipment
within appears worn.  You should type &OPRACTICE&z to see what you can learn,
and upon deciding what you would like to learn, &OPRACTICE <skill name>&z
to learn it.
~
~
0 0 13
D3
~
~
0 -1 13302
S
#13304
Preparing for Combat~
You are about to enter into an area with a few mobs in it.  If you have not
done so already you may wish to type &OCONFIG +AUTOLOOT&z and &OCONFIG +AUTOSAC
&zTo kill something simply type &OKILL&z and the name of what it is you wish
to kill.  After you kill something you can wear the equipment it was carrying
by typing &OWEAR&z and the name of the equipment.  To simplify things somewhat
you can also type &OWEAR ALL&z which will attempt to wear anything you are
carrying.
~
~
